                    <Typography variant="body" className="mb-6">
                      This comprehensive certification programme is designed for educators who are leading or aspiring to lead mental health and wellbeing initiatives in their schools. Whether you're a designated wellbeing lead, a senior leader with responsibility for pastoral care, or a teacher with a passion for promoting positive mental health, this programme will provide you with the knowledge, skills, and evidence-based strategies needed to create mentally healthy school environments.
